RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT a.CONTRACT_REF_NO, a.user_ref_no, a.product_code, b.product_description, a.counterparty, c.CUSTOMER_NAME1, a.branch FROM oltbs_contract a, oltms_product b, oltms_customer c WHERE a.product_code = b.product_code AND a.counterparty = c.CUSTOMER_NO AND a.BRANCH = global.current_branch AND a.module_code IN ('OL','LB','FC') ORDER BY CONTRACT_REF_NO
